title: Spanish Lamb Croquetas & Roast Tomato Salsa Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! With a crunchy, golden exterior and a savoury, meaty centre, every bite of these lamb croquetas will transport you to a bustling tapas bar right in the heart of Spain. If you need even more crunch, we've got you covered; these potatoes are boiled and then roasted to guarantee the crispiest potato experience you've ever had.
